and\": \"entire hooks factoryai-droid user-prompt-submit\"}\n  ]\n}]\n```\n\n## Changes\n\n### 1. `cmd/entire/cli/agent/factoryaidroid/hooks.go` — InstallHooks\n\nAfter the existing `sessionStart` hook installation (line ~158), add `userPromptSubmitCmd` to the `sessionStart` hook type:\n\n```go\n// Also install user-prompt-submit on SessionStart to ensure TurnStart fires\n// even when UserPromptSubmit doesn't (e.g., droid exec mode).\n// The user-prompt-submit handler gracefully handles SessionStart's stdin format\n// (userPromptSubmitRaw is a superset of sessionInfoRaw; Prompt defaults to \"\").\nif !hookCommandExists(sessionStart, userPromptSubmitCmd) {\n    sessionStart = addHookToMatcher(sessionStart, \"\", userPromptSubmitCmd)\n    count++\n}\n```\n\nNo other code changes needed:\n- **UninstallHooks** — `removeEntireHooks` already removes all `\"entire ...\"` commands from all hook types\n- **AreHooksInstalled** — Already checks for `\"entire hooks factoryai-droid stop\"` which is sufficient\n- **GetHookNames/GetSupportedHooks** — No changes; `user-prompt-submit` already exists as a subcommand\n- **ParseHookEvent** — No changes; `parseTurnStart` already handles missing `prompt` field\n\n### 2. `cmd/entire/cli/agent/factoryaidroid/hooks_test.go` — Update tests\n\n- Update `TestInstallHooks` to verify SessionStart has TWO commands (session-start + user-prompt-submit)\n- Add test: verify `parseTurnStart` handles SessionStart-format stdin (missing `prompt` field)\n- Update uninstall tests to verify both commands are removed from SessionStart\n\n### Files Summary\n\n| File | Change |\n|------|--------|\n| `cmd/entire/cli/agent/factoryaidroid/hooks.go` | Add `userPromptSubmitCmd` to `sessionStart` in InstallHooks (~3 lines) |\n| `cmd/entire/cli/agent/factoryaidroid/hooks_test.go` | Update install/uninstall tests |\n\n**No changes to:** `event.go`, `lifecycle.go`, `phase.go`, or any other agent's code.\n\n## Verification\n\n1. `mise run fmt && mise run lint` — passes\